docker-compose- tool by docker Inc
   
docker-compose -> manage multi container application

  clone repo-three tier architecture demo -instana robot 
docker compose up ->starts all your container
 browser- localhost:8080
docker compose down -.remove all your container
ctrl c->stop all your container

  need dockerfile
  docker yaml files->explain how to build,run your container 
  yaml file still reference to your dockerfile for docker image

    awesome compose -a lot of docker compose examples
    clone repo
    nginx/nodejs/redis
    cd nginx/nodejs/redis
    docker compose up
    browser-localhost:80
    without compose
    docker build web dockerfile loc
    docker build nginx dockerfile loc
    docker run -d -p 5000:81 web1
    docker run -d -p 5000:82 web2
    docker run -d -p 80:80 nginx

